Name: video_published_at
Description: The date and time when the video was published

Name: video_category_id
Description: Numeric ID representing the category of the video

Name: video_duration
Description: Duration of the video in ISO 8601 format (e.g. "PT10M15S" for 10 minutes and 15 seconds)

Name: video_view_count
Description: Total number of views for the video

Name: video_like_count

Name: video_comment_count

Name: channel_custom_url

Name: channel_view_count
Description: Total number of views across all videos on the channel

Name: channel_subscriber_count
Description: Total number of subscribers to the channel

Name: days_until_trend
Description: Total number of days until the video becomes a days_until_trend
